    <div class="section-hdr"><span>Critical</span></div>
    <div class="alert-row ar-r"><div class="ar-icon ai-r">!</div><div class="ar-body"><div class="ar-title">Jose Bernal & Habib Fazli — connect rate below 1% <span class="badge br" style="margin-left:5px">CT · HPH</span></div><div class="ar-detail">Both under 1% with 1,500+ dials. Below Average tier. Burning leads with zero return.</div><div class="ar-meta">Trigger: Connect Rate &lt;2% · Actual: 0.9%, 0.5%</div></div></div>
    <div class="alert-row ar-r"><div class="ar-icon ai-r">!</div><div class="ar-body"><div class="ar-title">Team show rate 48.6% — target 75% <span class="badge br" style="margin-left:5px">Team-wide</span></div><div class="ar-detail">267 demos booked, 102 completed. 165 no-shows MTD. Biggest revenue leak on the team.</div><div class="ar-meta">Trigger: Show Rate &lt;55% · Gap: 26.4pts</div></div></div>
    <div class="alert-row ar-r"><div class="ar-icon ai-r">!</div><div class="ar-body"><div class="ar-title">Samuel Michalcin, Jose Bernal, Caroline Christy — 3-day decline <span class="badge br" style="margin-left:5px">S8T · CT · HPH</span></div><div class="ar-detail">All three below KPI on dials and sets for 3 consecutive days. Pattern worsening not recovering.</div><div class="ar-meta">Trigger: Health Score Red 3+ consecutive days</div></div></div>
    <div class="alert-row ar-r"><div class="ar-icon ai-r">!</div><div class="ar-body"><div class="ar-title">jun tan* — 38.6 days stalled, no next meeting <span class="badge br" style="margin-left:5px">Suraj Bali · S8T</span></div><div class="ar-detail">$7,500 deal in pipeline since Feb 3. No follow-up scheduled. Expected close May 30.</div><div class="ar-meta">Trigger: Red Zone &gt;20 days · no next meeting</div></div></div>
    <div class="alert-row ar-r"><div class="ar-icon ai-r">!</div><div class="ar-body"><div class="ar-title">Jo Ogel — 30.6 days, expected close date missed <span class="badge br" style="margin-left:5px">Ben Barrales · S8T</span></div><div class="ar-detail">$5,500 in Funding stage. Expected close Feb 17 passed. Last contact Feb 11.</div><div class="ar-meta">Trigger: Expected close passed · still open</div></div></div>

    <div class="section-hdr"><span>Warnings</span></div>
    <div class="alert-row ar-y"><div class="ar-icon ai-y">!</div><div class="ar-body"><div class="ar-title">Conv→Set Rate 37.9% — Below Average <span class="badge by" style="margin-left:5px">Team-wide</span></div><div class="ar-detail">705 quality convos, only 267 booked. Reps are talking but not converting to demos.</div><div class="ar-meta">Trigger: Conv→Set &lt;40%</div></div></div>
    <div class="alert-row ar-y"><div class="ar-icon ai-y">!</div><div class="ar-body"><div class="ar-title">Emery Sage — $10K gross, $376 collected (4%) <span class="badge by" style="margin-left:5px">ECU</span></div><div class="ar-detail">Worst collection rate on the team. Needs investigation — is this deal actually closed?</div><div class="ar-meta">Trigger: Collection Rate &lt;50%</div></div></div>
